  "summary": "Typography hierarchy uses Avenir with specific weights, cases, and colors: H1 & H2 Avenir Black (Title Case/sentence), Body Avenir Roman black, ISI subheads Avenir Black ALL CAPS black, footnotes Avenir Book black; campaign and callouts Avenir Black ALL CAPS per palette."
